title: 'Contagion' Cast Issues PSAs About COVID-19
description: The cast of Steven Soderbergh’s 2011 pandemic film Contagion -- which has skyrocketed in popularity over the past several weeks -- has been releasing a series of public service announcements in regards to the ongoing spread of COVID-19. As reported by Gothami…
